# BetBudAI - Rebuilt from Scratch

> A high-performance AI-powered horse racing picks platform, rebuilt with modular architecture and refined by 5+ months of live operation learnings.

## Quick Start

### Local Development
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-org/BetBudAI.git
cd BetBudAI

# Backend
python -m venv .venv && source .venv/bin/activate
cd backend && pip install -r requirements.txt && flask run

# Frontend (new terminal)
cd frontend && npm install && npm start
```

Access at http://localhost:3000

### Docker
```bash
docker-compose up
```

